---
title: Crispy Chicken Tenders with BBQ Sauce plus Potato Wedges & Mixed Greens
description: For our fresh spin on this classic comfort staple, you'll coat chicken breast strips with tangy sour cream, then roll in light-as-air panko breadcrumbs. Fry to crunchy, golden perfection, and serve with a side of potato wedges, barbecue sauce for dipping, and a mixed green salad tossed in tangy balsamic vinaigrette for fresh, crisp contrast.
